  "subject": "1.0.0 and removed dcae.node.type and policy_get",
  "commit_message": "1.0.0 and removed dcae.node.type and policy_get\n\n* moved dcae.node.type and policy_get from lib\n  to dcaepolicy plugin and dcae.node.type\n* removed dependency on cloudify-plugins-common and requests packages\n* removed discovery logic\n  since the lib does not talk to policy-handler anymore\n  - happens in the new dcaepolicy plugin now\n* no more policy_apply_mode per policy node\n  - it is up to component's blueprint to decide how to notify\n    about policy change\n\nChange-Id: Ieefc3b5af1166a5c201574144fbf8c399e5ddc15\nIssue-Id: DCAEGEN2-62\nSigned-off-by: Alex Shatov <alexs@att.com>\n",
